Specialties: Broad experience in planning, implementation and monitoring & evaluation of development programmes. Areas of work include HIV/AIDS, Public Health, Child Protection, Emergency Response, Rural Development and Monitoring and Evaluation. Strong in evidenced-based programming. Proven ability to analyze and evaluate global, regional, country and community level data in order to provide programmers and funders with essential information for decision-making and advocacy purposes.
